review: Dr. Satyavani is an experienced and understanding doctor. She encourages normal delivery and expertly manages complications. She is the right person to make crucial decisions. We are confident we chose the best doctor for our newborn.

Dr Satyavani Rongali is perhaps one of the most patient doctors I have ever come across. She listens intently to all the concerns and has a thorough and holistic approach. Needless to say, her diagnosis has been point on. She does not try to set you up with expensive treatments, in fact she tries to prescribe as minimal medicines as possible! Had a really great experience :)
